---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout
    title="Desarrollo de Páginas Web | SEMTIC"
    description="Diseñamos páginas web modernas, rápidas y optimizadas para convertir visitas en clientes reales para tu empresa."
    image="https://semtic.cl/og-servicios.png"
>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section
        class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden"
        style="z-index: 10;"
    >
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse"
            style="animation-delay: 2s;"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1
                class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6 leading-tight"
            >
                Diseño de Páginas Web <br class="hidden lg:block"/><span class="text-gradient">Rápidas, Atractivas y Enfocadas en Vender.</span>
            </h1>
            <p
                class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed"
            >
                Tu sitio web no debe ser solo un folleto digital bonito; debe ser tu mejor vendedor trabajando para ti 24/7.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN DE DOLOR: EL PROBLEMA -->
    <section class="py-10 md:py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10;">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-10 md:p-16 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-[#0a0a1a]/80 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3/4 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#00f2ea] to-transparent opacity-50"></div>
                <h2 class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold mb-6 text-[#00f2ea] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">¿Sientes que tu web no está funcionando?</h2>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-light">
                    Una página lenta, desordenada o que no se ve bien en el celular <span class="text-[#00f2ea] font-medium">espanta a tus clientes en segundos.</span> Hoy en día, la primera impresión lo es todo. Si tu web no genera confianza instantánea, tu competencia se llevará la venta.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN DE SOLUCIONES -->
    <section class="py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.3), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.6));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            
            <!-- Encabezado de la sección -->
            <div class="text-center mb-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto hidden">
                <!-- Se oculta este header porque la sección de dolor ya cumple la función introductoria -->
            </div>

            <!-- Grid de Soluciones (3 Pilares) -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-10">
                <!-- Tarjeta 1 - UX/UI -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#4f46e5]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(79,70,229,0.3)]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5] border border-[#4f46e5]/20 group-hover:bg-[#4f46e5]/30 transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(79,70,229,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 15l-2 5L9 9l11 4-5 2zm0 0l5 5M7.188 2.239l.777 2.897M5.136 7.965l-2.898-.777M13.95 4.05l-2.122 2.122m-5.657 5.656l-2.12 2.122"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] leading-tight">Diseño Persuasivo (UX/UI)</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Estructuras limpias y modernas que guían al usuario de forma natural directamente hacia el botón de contacto o compra. No solo es verse bien, es funcionar bien.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tarjeta 2 - Velocidad -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#39ff14]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(57,255,20,0.3)]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#39ff14]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#39ff14]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14] border border-[#39ff14]/20 group-hover:bg-[#39ff14]/30 transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(57,255,20,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] leading-tight">Velocidad y Rendimiento</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Sitios optimizados técnicamente para cargar en milisegundos. Si tu página vuela, cumples con las exigencias de Google y tus clientes no se van. Landings ultra rápidas y Ecommerces 100% autoadministrables.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tarjeta 3 - Mobile-First -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#00f2ea]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,242,234,0.3)]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00f2ea]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00f2ea]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#00f2ea] border border-[#00f2ea]/20 group-hover:bg-[#00f2ea]/30 transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(0,242,234,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] leading-tight">100% Adaptables (Mobile-First)</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Tu negocio en cualquier pantalla. El sitio se verá y funcionará perfecto tanto en un teléfono móvil como en una tablet o computadora de escritorio.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN 3: CTA Final -->
    <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.8), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.95));">
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full max-w-lg h-64 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[150px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-tight">
                <span class="text-white">Estructura, velocidad y funcionalidad</span> <br class="hidden md:block"/> <span class="text-gradient hover-glow">pensadas para resultados reales.</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <a href="https://wa.me/56988169404?text=Hola,%20quisiera%20conversar%20sobre%20la%20estrategia%20para%20crear%20mi%20nueva%20página%20web" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 md:px-14 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#25D366] to-[#00f2ea] rounded-full text-[#050511] font-extrabold text-sm md:text-xl tracking-[0.05em] shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(0,242,234,0.3)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 uppercase group">
                    💻 Cotizar mi Nueva Web
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
